	(55,129,'Amazon','B00WBJGUA2','','Anonymous User','Nest Cam Security Camera','nest-security-cam','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Nest Cam Security Camera is a good option as far as in home security camera go. This camera offers 24/7 live streaming to your smart phone, night vision, motion and sound alerts and more. It is a good option for those who aren’t necessarily trying to be sneaky, but just want to keep an eye on their homes, and offers a lot of versatility in use. To that end, users seem to generally be in agreement that this is a helpful product, but no reliable as a security camera or baby monitor, and is better suited to keeping an eye on pets or the home in general while away.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Offers 24/7 live streaming and adjustable controls from the user’s smart phone</p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Can/will alert your phone if it detects motion or sound</p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Offers clear nighttime vision when the lights are off, in order to continue to accurately monitor goings on in your home at all times.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Nest Cam\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"NC1102ES\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"NC1102ES\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"6.6 X 3.8 X 6.5 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"3.9 X 6.6 X 6.9 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1.8 Pound\"}]',199.00,170.00,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Nest-NC1102ES-Cam-Security-Camera/dp/B00WBJGUA2%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00WBJGUA2','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.25\",\"counter\":2},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4,\"counter\":1775,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Nest-NC1102ES-Cam-Security-Camera\\/dp\\/B00WBJGUA2\\/tag=\"},{\"key\":\"CNET\",\"value\":4.5,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.cnet.com\\/products\\/nest-