	(61,134,'Amazon','B0013BKDO8','','Anonymous User','AcuRite Indoor Humidity Monitor (00613A1)','acurite-indoor-humidity-monitor','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The AcuRite Indoor Humidity Monitor is a device which tracks both a space’s temperature, as well as its humidity levels. This device allows you to see what a specific room or space’s temperature and humidity levels are at — at any given time — thereby allowing for consistent climate, which can be especially important for those who posses objects subject to distortion in varying climates. Apart from simply telling you what the temperature and humidity levels of a space are in the present time however, this device also gives you a reading on the highs and lows (both in temperature and humidity), for each day as well. Overall, this product is liked by users, generally receiving a 4.5 stars (out of 5), with users claiming that this product is fairly reliable for it’s price range.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><b>.</b> AcuRite accurately displays both the temperature and humidity of a room or space.</p><p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>.</b> AcuRite records the daily highs and lows of a space so you can check them later.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>. </b>Long battery life</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Chaney Instruments\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"00613A1\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"613\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Silver\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"3.06 X 1.29 X 2.45 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"1.2 X 3.1 X 4.3 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.2 Pound\"}]',12.99,7.64,1,'http://amzn.to/1JgbUQh','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.50\",\"counter\":2},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4.5,\"counter\":8286,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/amzn.to\\/1njfDmu\"},{\"key\":\"Home Depot\",\"value\